  <name>FreeFlume</name>
  <summary>Fast native desktop YT client</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      FreeFlume is a fast, native C++/Qt6 desktop YT client for Linux. It
      uses yt-dlp for extraction and libmpv for playback, with search,
      subscriptions, playlists, history, downloads, SponsorBlock, picture-in-picture
      and a configurable player.
    </p>
